.DT
crawl
Discworld command help
crawl

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
crawl - Allows you to move using only your arms.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
crawl
crawl stop
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5
This command allows you to crawl, for example to get through certain low exits or as an alternative movement method should your legs be unavailable.  While you are crawling, you can only move very slowly.  There are also some factors that influence your speed, all of them related to your hands.
.EP

.SH Example
.SP 5 5
> crawl

You lower yourself to the ground, preparing to crawl like you've never crawled before.

> crawl stop

You stop crawling around and get up to your feet.  Your tortured arms thank you for this.
.EP
